ived by the Server (e.g., as a result of radio collisions),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the next received message will make up for the lost messages,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"carrying cumulative values of the field."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A new transaction is started when this field is set to "},{"code":"true","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"or when the last message of the transaction was sent 6 or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"more seconds earlier.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This defaults to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"false"},{"type":"text","text":", which means that each new message will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"receive a new transaction identifier (if not set explicitly)."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"references":{"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh":{"abstract":[{"text":"Provision, configure and control Bluetooth mesh devices with nRF Mesh library.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","title":"NordicMesh","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh"},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/LightLightnessLinearSetUnacknowledged":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/LightLightnessLinearSetUnacknowledged","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/lightlightnesslinearsetunacknowledged","abstract":[],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"LightLightnessLinearSetUnacknowledged"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"LightLightnessLinearSetUnacknowledged"}],"title":"LightLightnessLinearSetUnacknowledged"},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/LightLightnessLinearSetUnacknowledged/continueTransaction":{"url":"\/doc